SEGUROS LUCKY SEVEN

119
00:14:02,683 --> 00:14:06,516
Tienes que...

120
00:14:08,225 --> 00:14:09,225
...despertar.

121
00:14:10,641 --> 00:14:11,850
Despertar.

122
00:14:20,516 --> 00:14:22,141
No te mueras.

